{"ayat_mp3":"https://everyayah.com/data/Alafasy_128kbps/002194.mp3","arabic":"ٱلشَّهۡرُ ٱلۡحَرَامُ بِٱلشَّهۡرِ ٱلۡحَرَامِ وَٱلۡحُرُمَٰتُ قِصَاصٞۚ فَمَنِ ٱعۡتَدَىٰ عَلَيۡكُمۡ فَٱعۡتَدُواْ عَلَيۡهِ بِمِثۡلِ مَا ٱعۡتَدَىٰ عَلَيۡكُمۡۚ وَٱتَّقُواْ ٱللَّهَ وَٱعۡلَمُوٓاْ أَنَّ ٱللَّهَ مَعَ ٱلۡمُتَّقِينَ","bengali":"সম্মানিত মাসই সম্মানিত মাসের বদলা। আর সম্মান রক্ষা করারও বদলা রয়েছে। বস্তুতঃ যারা তোমাদের উপর জবর দস্তি করেছে, তোমরা তাদের উপর জবরদস্তি কর, যেমন জবরদস্তি তারা করেছে তোমাদের উপর। আর তোমরা আল্লাহকে ভয় কর এবং জেনে রাখ, যারা পরহেযগার, আল্লাহ তাদের সাথে রয়েছেন।","english":"The sacred month is for the sacred month, and for the prohibited things, there is the Law of Equality (Qisas). Then whoever transgresses the prohibition against you, you transgress likewise against him. And fear Allah, and know that Allah is with Al-Muttaqun (the pious - see V)","wbw":[{"bengali":"মাস","english":"The month","en_t":"al-shahru","arabic":"ٱلشَّهۡرُ","ar_mp3":"https://words.audios.quranwbw.com/2/002_194_001.mp3"},{"bengali":"পবিত্র","english":"[the] sacred","en_t":"al-haramu","arabic":"ٱلۡحَرَامُ","ar_mp3":"https://words.audios.quranwbw.com/2/002_194_002.mp3"},{"bengali":"মাস বিনিময়ে","english":"(is) for the month","en_t":"bil-shahri","arabic":"بِٱلشَّهۡرِ","ar_mp3":"https://words.audios.quranwbw.com/2/002_194_003.mp3"},{"bengali":"পবিত্র","english":"[the] sacred","en_t":"al-harami","arabic":"ٱلۡحَرَامِ","ar_mp3":"https://words.audios.quranwbw.com/2/002_194_004.mp3"},{"bengali":"এবং সমস্ত পবিত্র বিষয় (লংঘনের)","english":"and for all the violations","en_t":"wal-hurumatu","arabic":"وَٱلۡحُرُمَٰتُ","ar_mp3":"https://words.audios.quranwbw.com/2/002_194_005.mp3"},{"bengali":"বদলা (রয়েছে)","english":"(is) legal retribution","en_t":"qisasun","arabic":"قِصَاصٞۚ","ar_mp3":"https://words.audios.quranwbw.com/2/002_194_006.mp3"},{"bengali":"যে তাই","english":"Then whoever","en_t":"famani","arabic":"فَمَنِ","ar_mp3":"https://words.audios.quranwbw.com/2/002_194_007.mp3"},{"bengali":"বাড়াবাড়ি করব